content: I think I'll go with the customized jewelry option. I've been looking at some online marketplaces and I found a similar necklace that I got for my sister's birthday, which was $75. I'm hoping to find something around that price range or a bit higher. By the way, I've been good about budgeting for gifts lately, except for one impulse buy last week when I saw a sale at my favorite bookstore - I got the book for $24 after a discount.
